<br>
today i was in df, quite a bit.  i found a rank 4 paladin fighting a berserker and his buffbot.  i got there after the paladin had killed the buffbot and had the berserker down to about 80%.  before we managed to kill the paladin, he killed the berserker.  i chalked this up to luck.  i'm rank 7 by the way.  the berserker is 10k short of rank 4.  eventually i get 3 shot killed by a rank 2 armsman.  401 + dot proc, 255 since i out of viewed him, 457, i mez and flee and the dot kills me.  /cheer<br>
<br>
